      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "VALIDATE (5) brought up his 31st career win last start at Q Lakeside (30.45). Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Sure to prove hard to beat. APACHE TIGER (8) had been in great form but was out of the placings last run, finishing fifth (30.91) in a NG at Taree Super Track. Normally safe to begin but shuffled back last time off the low draw. Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Cannot be taken lightly. PAX BOSTONIA (2) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish 1.5 lengths away in second (29.53) behind Zipping Ariel at Wentworth Park. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and a minor placing from four starts. Bold showing expected. NON STOP WHISKEY (1) recorded a 2.75 lengths win (30.06) in a Grade 5 last time at this track. Has an unbeaten record from this draw, scoring four times.",
